close_reason: "Fixed: deriveExtensionCapabilities now adds schema when any blueprint.commands[].flags !== undefined, mirroring the loader's registerCommand-flags guard, so a derived manifest no longer under-grants and fails activation. Covered by a new unit test and pinned by the describeExtensionBlueprint inline-flags parity test."
